description:

Before the elite stuck it’s vangs into all aspects of life to make this mix of grey in everything.

They have different standards yes I just said that. Equal in my heart and their value to life  but will possess different GOD GIVIN  strengths and that’s what I as a parent have to nurture

Matter a fact , I will give a recent example later today of a parental situation that happened recently with my children , and how I differentiate between the two when it comes to certain things.
